<h4><a href="https://www.donews.com/news/detail/1/3115045.html">亚朵旗下首家 ZHotel 在北京开业</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1369060" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/W020200927365227971069.jpg" alt="" width="1269" height="847" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/W020200927365227971069.jpg 1269w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/W020200927365227971069-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/W020200927365227971069-768x513.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/W020200927365227971069-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1269px) 100vw, 1269px" /></p>
<p>DoNews 消息，昨天，亚朵集团旗下 Z 世代生活方式品牌「北京望京 798ZHotel」首家门店在北京开业，这是亚朵宣布加注中高端市场后首个落地的高端品牌。</p>
<p>在接下来一年里，ZHotel 还会在上海的云海大厦和外滩的沙美大楼相继开业两家门店。</p>
<h4><a href="https://cn.businessoffashion.com/articles/news-analysis/1285480-chanel-ugg-cn">香奈儿发行 6 亿欧元绿色环保债券</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1369061" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/chanel-price-hikes.jpg" alt="" width="1230" height="820" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/chanel-price-hikes.jpg 1230w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/chanel-price-hikes-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/chanel-price-hikes-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/chanel-price-hikes-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1230px) 100vw, 1230px" /></p>
<p>BoF 援引路透社消息指，法国奢侈品牌香奈儿发行了 6 亿欧元的可持续发展债券，该债券条款与其环保目标相关，部分收益可能用于投资开发塑料或皮革替代品的初创企业。</p>
<p>根据交易结构，如果公司在企业内部或供应链方面没有达到一定的减排目标，那么在债券到期时，香奈儿将需要支付一笔溢价。</p>
<h4><a href="https://hypebeast.cn/2020/9/adidas-disney-pixar-toy-story-collaboration-release-info">阿迪达斯推出《玩具总动员》联名系列</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1369062" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/adidas-disney-pixar-toy-story-collaboration-release-info-2.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="683" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/adidas-disney-pixar-toy-story-collaboration-release-info-2.jpg 1024w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/adidas-disney-pixar-toy-story-collaboration-release-info-2-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/adidas-disney-pixar-toy-story-collaboration-release-info-2-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></p>
<p>Hypebeast 消息，阿迪达斯推出和《玩具总动员》联名系列，将皮克斯经典 IP 和 Dame 7、adizero Football Cleats、Deep Threat、NMD_R1 等鞋款结合。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1369063" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/pixar.jpg" alt="" width="1498" height="658" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/pixar.jpg 1498w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/pixar-360x158.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/pixar-768x337.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/pixar-1024x450.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1498px) 100vw, 1498px" /></p>
<p>除此之外，阿迪达斯还特地以剧中经典的红色星星皮球为主题，制作了一个同样造型的篮球。该系列将于 10 月 1 日开始发售。</p>
<h4><a href="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/gl6ENbKBmhC6bwJXGEAW3g">《夺冠》等 5 部电影入选重点作品版权保护预警名单</a></h4>
<p>国家版权局消息，《夺冠》《急先锋》《我和我的家乡》《姜子牙》和《一点就到家》入选「2020 年度第六批重点作品版权保护预警名单」。</p>
<p>保护措施具体如下：直接提供内容的网络服务商在影片上映期内不得提供版权保护预警名单内的作品；提供存储空间的网络服务商应禁止用户上传版权保护预警名单内的作品；相关网络服务提供商应当加快处理版权保护预警名单内作品权利人关于删除侵权内容或断开侵权链接的通知。</p>
